{
  "stem": "18813.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were coming home for lunch because it wasn't too far to go, and the-- when I was taking the business school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was the afternoon, in the evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So and after that, we are going home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were close.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have the freedom what the kids have now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My coming was-- my mother and father expected me to be home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you have any hobbies or interests?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very guarded, spoiled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just going out with the kids, and sometimes going places where my parents didn't know where I went.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hope they aren't in another life to see the tape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just walking with boys, but under the bridge where nobody can see it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we all were, you know, a group of kids going together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the parents didn't-- they, they shouldn't have done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quiet.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I had to answer, I had to answer-- respect for the mother and father, and [SIGHS] lots of friends.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother and father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would both know my-- if there was a problem, then they knew about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite religious because we had the Jewish maid, who was cooking that while mother was in the business from 8 o'clock in the morning until late, and eating late, late dinner.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Shabbos was-- Friday night dinner was, you know, lighting the candles, and-- a typically religious home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fish, soup, meat, and vegetables, and that's it, whatever-- pastry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I [SIGHS] didn't feel like to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when you grow up, you have something else in mind than to go the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was going with my friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were going out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was a respect for my mother and father.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
